features: ANTI-REFLECTIVE TECHNOLOGY - This new treatment significantly decreases reflections and increases the light transmitted to improve your screen’s clarity and enrich the color depth and vibrancy of the images on your screen. Pro-level optics for your new iPhone 14 Plus

MAXIMUM IMPACT PROTECTION - Glass XTR2 is made with shock-absorbing Hexiom impact technology that has an adhesive, honey-comb like structure that strengthens the surface of the screen protector, making it over 10% stronger than the original.

ULTRA SENSITIVE, EDGE-TO-EDGE - Glass XTR2 has maximum touch sensitivity which was engineered for mobile gaming, and stretches edge-to-edge for true, uninterrupted cover, including over the front phone sensors.

ANTI-DUST INSTALLATION: XTR2's revolutionary new anti-dust adhesive combined with our EZ Apply installation method means perfect, dust-free installations. Every time. And the install tray is made with 50% recycled materials.
body.description: The strongest screen protection just got stronger. Glass XTR2 is made with Hexiom impact technology that makes 10% stronger than its predecssor. Revolutionary new anti-reflective technology significantly reduces reflections on your screen while letting more light transmit through the protector for clear, precise images and color quality. ZAGG also added enhanced Eyesafe blue light technology that filters 40% of intense blue light (435-440nm) from your device screen. Glass XTR2 is ideal for gamers with an ultra-smooth, touch-sensitive surface that reduces friction as you move your finger across the surface of the screen. A new, world-first anti-dust adhesive combined with ZAGG's EZ Apply install make installations perfect and dust-free. Every time. Glass XTR2 has a limited lifetime warranty, and sets a new premium standard for screen protection.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 7, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Updated review: I dropped my phone flat on the screen and this screen protector saved my actual screen. This product comes with a plastic tool that helps you align the screen protector perfectly, DO NOT throw it away because the replacement they send using your warranty does not come with one. I didn’t have it even at first so I took it off and applied it again I much have touched the adhesive because now I have a bubble on a corner of my screen. So keep the tool this comes with or you’ll be sorry.I use ZAGG because of the lifetime warranty. Your screen protector will eventually crack or chip so it’s pretty much necessary. I was about to purchase this off their website and found it wayyyy cheaper on Amazon. Installation was easy, love the plastic piece that helps you align the protector perfectly. Make sure you push the bubbles out and if you’re left with air at the ends it’s probably just air under the top layer. Peel the top layer off and there you go!

I have always used ZAGG products since I can remember. I have a case and this fit perfectly within the case borders. Very durable. I accidentally put my phone in my pocket where I usually keep my keys and there were no scratches. I’ve had the protector for some time and I still don’t see any scratches or wear. My screen is still responsive as if it wasn’t there.
